## 🧠 What it does
Students can ask questions in natural language:
- "Mera attendance dikhao"
- "DBMS mein kitne marks hain?"
- "Aaj ki class kab hai?"

AI converts questions to SQL and fetches real data.

## 🏗️ Tech Stack
| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Frontend | Next.js + TypeScript + Tailwind |
| Backend | FastAPI + SQLAlchemy + JWT |
| Database | PostgreSQL (Supabase) |
| AI | LLM + Text-to-SQL |
| Deployment | Vercel + Supabase |

## ✨ Features
- 🤖 AI Chat with Text-to-SQL
- 📊 Attendance tracking
- 📝 Marks & grades
- 📅 Timetable
- 🔐 JWT Authentication
